      <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Text_DBknuW">
        <bpmn:text>Based on the Reason of Visit; Agent retrieves, analyses and summarizes the Consultation History of the Patient. It will also find out relevant Test reports for Doctor's reference.  Makes use of Perplexity AI Web Summary to provide recommendation to the Doctor .</bpmn:text>
